      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are resources but it doesn't change the reality. the money is gone. the reputation is destroyed. it's not just a \"difficult period\" for me, it feels like my whole identity was built on this and now it's just... empty. every time i try to think about \"one step at a time,\" i just see the mountain of debt and the look on my family's faces when they realize it's all over. it's like there's just no version of the future where i'm not a walking disaster.",
